data.description: The perfect place to call home, with its location close to Highways 287, I-20, and Hwy. 360, and minutes from both Dallas and Fort Worth. Zoned to the reputable Mansfield ISD, the community is close to local schools, as well as shopping, dining, and entertainment. In this Silver Oak Community, you will find this luxurious home at an affordable price. This stunning home is DR Horton's Granbury floorplan featuring 4 bedrooms (front bedroom can serve as a study), 2 bathrooms, with wood-look ceramic tile throughout, state-of-the-art energy efficiency features, green energy efficient solar panels, 3-car garage, and industry-leading ‘Home is Connected’ Smart Home Technology. Meticulously maintained, ready for immediate move-in! You don't want to miss this!
